♪Cold eyes♪

77
00:06:14,937 --> 00:06:19,536
♪Searching for traces of light
in the dark♪

78
00:06:19,537 --> 00:06:24,586
♪Learning to fade from the crowd♪

79
00:06:24,587 --> 00:06:27,311
♪The endless dark clouds♪

80
00:06:27,312 --> 00:06:29,061
♪I miss you so much♪

81
00:06:29,062 --> 00:06:32,674
♪Longing for an echo of salvation♪

82
